{"tid":1496400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要]請各位手足不要參加825嘅犬隻家屬集會","createTime":"2019-08-22T13:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T15:03:21.000Z","uid":35776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e2563fa83b7ee87d2aeeabd641e89815a1c39f3f","tid":1496400,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:46:28.000Z","msg":"我認真希望大家唔好去825個家屬聚會，我地無謂幫人做佈景板，留個場畀真正嘅家屬發揮。<br />\n<br />\n人多：警察都有好多好人&gt;唔應該針對整個警隊&gt;吹和風扮friend&gt;冷卻降溫&gt;個別事件&gt;不了了之無法追究&gt;港共大清算捉人判刑乜都齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家真係想跟呢條storyline去發生嘅，我絕對唔阻止大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />connect埋警犬老婆<br />\n<br />\n另外自己睇睇下圖第三點，完全伏到仆街，市民同警察要對話只需要PPRB正確履行職責就可以做到，所謂成立平台就係跟從林鄭成立平台嘅路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去行。<br />\n<br />\n所以，敬告所以手足：825係屬於警察家屬嘅集會，我地唔參加，唔推動，表明該集會不屬於整個反送中運動所發起嘅行動。 我恐防有和理非市民被誤導，故此特意說破825集會嘅毒計，林鄭盡快動員愛國陣營不少於撐警集會嘅人數，人數過少就好難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTv985P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTv985P.jpg&h=23ca47a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50349a34dd936be1f80267d0f9d16e856d2a9b69","tid":1496400,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:49:29.000Z","msg":"入去影相起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n禍，必及<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［置頂]聽晚識巴絲教學，同場仲有快速單身配對！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496384</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2224